00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:20,079 --> 00:00:21,399
I was wrong!

2
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:24,079
I was wrong! Don't take me!

3
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:25,320
Don't take me! I was wrong!

4
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,519
Master Wang.

5
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:28,079
Master Wang!

6
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:30,960
Why are you panicking?

7
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,719
A wealthy merchant like you

8
00:00:32,799 --> 00:00:34,000
keeps no lamps in your courtyard.

9
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:35,600
You made me fall into the pond.

10
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:36,840
My clothes are soaked.

11
00:00:53,660 --> 00:00:59,980
=The Tang Mist S1=

12
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:20,460
=Episode 3=

13
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,199
Just now,

14
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,599
you said you were wrong.

15
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,759
What exactly did you do wrong?

16
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:28,439
Well...

17
00:02:29,159 --> 00:02:30,199
To answer you, Official Di,

18
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,879
Qi Changshun

19
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,439
treated me like his own brother.

20
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,319
Two years ago,

21
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:38,000
the court urgently needed salt.

22
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,319
I should have escorted the shipment,

23
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:41,960
but unfortunately,

24
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,560
I broke my leg.

25
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,080
Who knew

26
00:02:46,159 --> 00:02:48,000
the ship would sink?

27
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,639
If I had boarded that day,

28
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,240
I would have been the one to die.

29
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:05,479
Qi

30
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,280
died in my place.

31
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,439
I have been ashamed

32
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,680
and unable to find peace ever since.

33
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,199
It was all my fault.

34
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,879
Qi built Hengshun Salt Bureau

35
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:20,280
from nothing.

36
00:03:21,599 --> 00:03:22,199
So

37
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,080
after I took over

38
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,479
Hengshun Salt Bureau,

39
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,840
I never changed its name.

40
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,479
I only wished

41
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:31,840
to comfort Qi's soul

42
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,439
in the afterlife.

43
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:38,120
Everyone in town is saying

44
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,080
the water ghost

45
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,840
is the vengeful spirit of the Qi family.

46
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:44,599
What do you think?

47
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,000
Was there an injustice?

48
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,439
If there truly was,

49
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,599
then Qi must still blame me.

50
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,800
If he comes to take my life,

51
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,840
I am willing to go down there

52
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:02,479
and keep Qi company.

53
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:08,639
Where were the Qi father and son buried?

54
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,520
Buried...

55
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,560
Buried at...

56
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,279
And you call him your brother?

57
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,639
You even forgot where he was buried.

58
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,519
Perhaps Master Wang

59
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:26,279
has been busy with salt affairs

60
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,279
and has not visited for some time.

61
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,600
That is why

62
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,439
he cannot recall it.

63
00:04:38,839 --> 00:04:40,040
I am ashamed.

64
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,480
I truly...

65
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,879
I truly have been too busy

66
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,000
to spare the time.

67
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:49,580
(Ruanjiang County Bureau)

68
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,800
Who comes to file a grievance?

69
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,079
I am Du Ruo.

70
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,240
I seek justice for my husband.

71
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,319
Du Ruo?

72
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:06,839
Aren't you the new bride

73
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:08,199
of Wang Xian, Young Master
of Hengshun Salt Bureau?

74
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,279
I am Du Ruo.

75
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:17,160
I seek justice for my husband, Qi Feng.

76
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,160
What?

77
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:19,279
Didn't

78
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,079
Qi Feng die

79
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:21,839
when the ship sank two years ago?

80
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:26,199
I thought

81
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:28,439
we had been parted forever too.

82
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,800
But Heaven showed mercy

83
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,439
and let us meet again.

84
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,680
What injustice did he suffer?

85
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,480
He was burned to death.

86
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:41,000
When?

87
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:43,480
Two hours ago.

88
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,279
Where?

89
00:05:45,879 --> 00:05:47,040
Tell me everything.

90
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,040
Two days ago,

91
00:05:50,199 --> 00:05:52,519
we agreed to meet tonight at Buxianxian.

92
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:57,040
- But when I arrived,
- Let's go.

93
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,759
I saw two people setting fire

94
00:05:58,759 --> 00:06:00,279
to Buxianxian.

95
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,800
Qi Feng.

96
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,279
Qi Feng!

97
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:16,879
Ruo!

98
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,160
Go!

99
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,959
Qi Feng!

100
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,720
Ruo!

101
00:06:24,759 --> 00:06:25,720
Don't come closer!

102
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,519
Don't come closer!

103
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:28,920
Ruo!

104
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,519
Qi Feng!

105
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:48,120
Did you see

106
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,920
what those two looked like?

107
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,560
Even in death, I could never forget.

108
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,920
There is soot
in the victim's mouth and nose.

109
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,759
The skin is badly charred.

110
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,680
There are localized burns and blisters.

111
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:28,160
Parts of the skin
have shriveled and peeled away.

112
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:30,480
All signs point to death by burning.

113
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,600
Just as Du Ruo said,

114
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,759
the deceased was indeed male.

115
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,720
The body measured six chi in length.

116
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:52,480
Official Di,

117
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,800
there is

118
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,480
something strange about this fire.

119
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:09,399
Official Di, these are letters
personally written by Qi Feng.

120
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,279
Please have a look.

121
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,000
Ruo.

122
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,319
(If this letter reaches you...)

123
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,360
(After surviving the disaster at sea,)

124
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,759
(I thought our fate had come to an end.)

125
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:27,120
(By fortune, I survived.)

126
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,279
Ruo.

127
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:30,839
If this letter reaches you...

128
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,200
once the troubles
of this world are settled,

129
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,480
we will enjoy the beauty
of life together again.

130
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,600
Qi Feng

131
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:44,399
appeared half a month ago?

132
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:46,000
Yes.

133
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,480
If he was still alive,

134
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,279
why did he wait two years

135
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:54,559
before showing himself?

136
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:59,200
He said...

137
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,679
There was something suspicious

138
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:01,480
about the sinking
of the Qi family's ship.

139
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,639
Before uncovering the truth,

140
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:04,879
I could not reveal myself.

141
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,759
We only resumed contact

142
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,120
through letters half a month ago.

143
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:20,320
(Ruo. Meet me at Buxianxian
two nights from now. It is urgent.)

144
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,360
Buxianxian.

145
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,080
Urgent.

146
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,759
What did Qi Feng discover?

147
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,840
Before he could say anything,

148
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:29,879
he...

149
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:38,519
Qi Feng

150
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,600
is the water ghost?

151
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:47,559
No.

152
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,120
No, he is not.

153
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,320
(River Transport Order)
The water ghost claims lives.

154
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,399
The transport order bears the name Qi.

155
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,240
Qi Feng appeared half a month ago.

156
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,000
That matches exactly
with the time of death

157
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,080
of the first victim

158
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,320
in the water ghost case.

159
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,720
It must be Qi Feng.

160
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,720
That is only speculation.

161
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,200
The handwriting above

162
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,759
was not written by the same person.

163
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,340
(River Transport Order. Qi Feng)

164
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,519
If Qi Feng wished to hide his identity,

165
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,759
forging different handwriting
would have been easy.

166
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,639
Lin is right.

167
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,840
Without proof,

168
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,399
we cannot make reckless conclusions.

169
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,039
Du Ruo

170
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:28,320
has truly suffered greatly.

171
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,879
Tomorrow was supposed
to be her wedding day,

172
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,080
yet such a tragedy happened instead.

173
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:45,399
Ruo.

174
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,799
The dead cannot return to life.

175
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:53,000
If you want to cry,

176
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,960
then cry.

177
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:57,799
Do not keep it all buried inside.

178
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,799
Seeing you like this

179
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,399
only pains me even more.

180
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,759
I will leave you alone now.

181
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,840
Qi Feng is the water ghost.

182
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,639
Ruo,

183
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,759
when did you find out?

184
00:11:31,519 --> 00:11:32,679
When he killed the second man.

185
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:56,600
Qi Feng was an exceptional swimmer.

186
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,759
He survived the sinking.

187
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:00,759
After returning to Ruanjiang,

188
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:02,480
he uncovered the truth
behind what happened.

189
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:04,440
He wanted revenge

190
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:06,080
for Uncle Qi and Aunt Qi,

191
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,399
and for all the innocent souls

192
00:12:08,399 --> 00:12:09,600
who died unjustly back then.

193
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,039
Ruo!

194
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,480
Father.

195
00:12:17,519 --> 00:12:19,080
Qi Feng is the water ghost.

196
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,720
Qi Feng is the water ghost.

197
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,159
Ruo.

198
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:38,200
You have suffered so much.

199
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:41,879
Father,

200
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,639
I have already lost

201
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,639
the man I loved most.

202
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,159
I want you to stay with me forever.

203
00:12:50,919 --> 00:12:52,519
I cannot lose you too.

204
00:12:53,759 --> 00:12:54,559
I cannot.

205
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,120
Father will stay with you forever.

206
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,360
Forever.

207
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,399
Master Wang.

208
00:13:08,519 --> 00:13:08,840
No...

209
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:09,759
No sign of him.

210
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,000
How about Yihua House?

211
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,919
They said he left two days ago.

212
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,639
Keep searching.

213
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:14,879
Keep searching!

214
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,080
Master,

215
00:13:16,399 --> 00:13:17,279
report it to the authorities.

216
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:17,960
With the water ghost...

217
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:18,720
Shut up!

218
00:13:19,519 --> 00:13:20,440
It cannot be the water ghost.

219
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,720
Absolutely not!

220
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,919
I have seen plenty of corpses,

221
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:28,399
but this is my first time
seeing someone burned to death.

222
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,000
This is...

223
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,159
Strange.

224
00:13:53,320 --> 00:13:54,200
Why do both victims

225
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,600
have this kind of fiber on them?

226
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:58,759
What fiber?

227
00:13:59,519 --> 00:14:00,000
Official Di,

228
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:00,799
look.

229
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:06,399
This is...

230
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:11,759
Hemp rope.

231
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,080
(They were stuffed into)

232
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,720
(fishing nets woven from hemp rope,)

233
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:40,080
(and weighed down before being drowned.)

234
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:43,559
(This is the true face
of the water ghost.)

235
00:14:51,039 --> 00:14:51,799
Official Di.

236
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,639
Official Di.

237
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:54,399
You must help me, Official Di.

238
00:14:54,399 --> 00:14:56,399
My son is missing.

239
00:14:56,399 --> 00:14:57,200
Missing?

240
00:14:58,919 --> 00:15:00,080
That Yihua House...

241
00:15:02,159 --> 00:15:03,480
What I mean is,

242
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,360
the Young Master often stays out

243
00:15:05,399 --> 00:15:06,399
all night.

244
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:08,879
So when he hadn't shown up
these past few days,

245
00:15:08,919 --> 00:15:10,240
I did not think much of it.

246
00:15:10,759 --> 00:15:11,159
But

247
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:13,519
today is his wedding day.

248
00:15:13,639 --> 00:15:15,480
There is no way he would not show up.

249
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,159
Wasn't the marriage already called off?

250
00:15:17,679 --> 00:15:19,360
Perhaps he could not accept it

251
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,840
and went somewhere else to drink.

252
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:22,039
Reporting to Official Di,

253
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,919
we have searched everywhere.

254
00:15:27,799 --> 00:15:29,320
When and where

255
00:15:29,559 --> 00:15:30,879
was Wang Xian last seen?

256
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,440
Two days ago.

257
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,320
The Young Master said

258
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:35,720
he was going to Yi...

259
00:15:35,879 --> 00:15:36,879
Going to Yihua House

260
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:37,519
to see Cui Lan.

261
00:15:40,639 --> 00:15:41,279
No, wait.

262
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,000
Official Di,

263
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:44,200
the last person

264
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:45,720
my son

265
00:15:45,759 --> 00:15:47,200
should have seen was Du Ruo.

266
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,720
Missing?

267
00:15:55,399 --> 00:15:56,320
Two days ago,

268
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,559
did you see Wang Xian?

269
00:16:04,159 --> 00:16:04,960
No.

270
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,519
I am here.

271
00:16:14,519 --> 00:16:16,399
You need not worry about anything.

272
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:18,679
That night,

273
00:16:19,240 --> 00:16:20,879
what exactly happened?

274
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:34,120
Please seek justice for me, Official Di.

275
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,960
What makes him better than me?

276
00:16:58,639 --> 00:17:00,320
Qi Feng was kindhearted,

277
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,200
upright,

278
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,320
and honorable in all he did.

279
00:17:04,519 --> 00:17:05,440
His love for me

280
00:17:06,039 --> 00:17:07,160
was beyond question.

281
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,480
And what about you?

282
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,680
Cruel and calculating,

283
00:17:11,799 --> 00:17:13,200
yet cowardly to the core.

284
00:17:14,759 --> 00:17:15,799
You wanted to marry me

285
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:17,880
for no reason other than to prove

286
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:18,799
that you were better than him,

287
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:21,279
to satisfy that pathetic

288
00:17:21,279 --> 00:17:23,160
and laughable pride of yours.

289
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:24,720
How could you

290
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:26,559
ever compare to him?

291
00:17:32,319 --> 00:17:33,279
What is this?

292
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:35,799
Give it to me.

293
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,279
Bring it here!

294
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,319
Give it to me!

295
00:17:42,559 --> 00:17:43,119
Give me the letter!

296
00:17:43,119 --> 00:17:43,640
Let go!

297
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:44,000
Give it to me!

298
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:44,799
Let go!

299
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,180
(Ruo. Meet me at Buxianxian
two nights from now. It is urgent.)

300
00:17:53,180 --> 00:17:54,480
(Qi Feng)

301
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,279
Qi Feng?

302
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,200
Qi Feng?

303
00:17:58,920 --> 00:17:59,720
Impossible.

304
00:18:00,480 --> 00:18:01,319
Impossible.

305
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,160
It's been two years.

306
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:09,480
I thought your illness

307
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:10,000
was only an excuse

308
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,200
to avoid marrying me.

309
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:12,319
I never imagined

310
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:13,400
Qi Feng was actually still alive.

311
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,759
You two truly disgust me.

312
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:17,279
You were willing to risk

313
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:19,440
your entire Du family for his sake?

314
00:18:20,759 --> 00:18:21,559
Buxianxian?

315
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:22,759
What?

316
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:24,200
Were you planning

317
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,160
to elope before our wedding?

318
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,119
Did you tell Qi Feng

319
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:29,119
about what happened between us

320
00:18:29,119 --> 00:18:29,960
at Buxianxian?

321
00:18:35,319 --> 00:18:36,440
No wonder the shaman said

322
00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:37,640
he wasn't drowned to death.

323
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:38,640
He was burned alive.

324
00:18:41,319 --> 00:18:42,440
If drowning could not kill him,

325
00:18:45,839 --> 00:18:47,759
then I would burn him to death.

326
00:19:18,559 --> 00:19:20,319
The two people who killed Qi Feng

327
00:19:20,319 --> 00:19:21,599
worked for Wang Xian?

328
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,680
Yes.

329
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,000
Why did you not say so last night?

330
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:27,960
Wang Xian

331
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,359
used my father's life

332
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:30,279
to force me to marry him.

333
00:19:30,960 --> 00:19:32,680
Then he burned Qi Feng alive.

334
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,680
There is nothing he would not do.

335
00:19:35,039 --> 00:19:35,279
I...

336
00:19:37,359 --> 00:19:39,160
Qi Feng is the water ghost?

337
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,200
Yes.

338
00:19:43,119 --> 00:19:44,559
Qi Feng is the water ghost.

339
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,720
Then if he is already dead,

340
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:52,200
why did you continue hiding
the truth for him?

341
00:19:54,119 --> 00:19:54,960
Qi Feng

342
00:19:55,839 --> 00:19:56,720
is the water ghost?

343
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:58,720
No.

344
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,039
No, he is not.

345
00:20:03,160 --> 00:20:04,960
Qi Feng disguised himself
as the water ghost to kill.

346
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,279
He was already guilty
in the eyes of the law.

347
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:07,839
I feared the Bureau

348
00:20:07,839 --> 00:20:08,960
would no longer

349
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:09,720
value his life,

350
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,920
so I lied.

351
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,720
Official Di,

352
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:16,720
Wang Xian must have fled out of fear.

353
00:20:17,400 --> 00:20:19,200
Please seek justice
for Qi Feng, Official Di.

354
00:20:28,519 --> 00:20:30,279
I do not think Wang Xian is missing.

355
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:32,680
Qi Feng's body
must have been discovered,

356
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:34,279
and Wang Dingrong hid him away.

357
00:20:34,519 --> 00:20:35,480
Whether it is true or not,

358
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,759
our priority

359
00:20:36,759 --> 00:20:37,599
is to find him.

360
00:20:38,039 --> 00:20:39,880
Since Wang Dingrong has made his move,

361
00:20:40,119 --> 00:20:41,400
we shall respond in kind.

362
00:20:42,359 --> 00:20:43,400
Whether he is truly missing

363
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:45,000
or merely staging an act of self pity,

364
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:47,240
one wrong step in this move

365
00:20:48,039 --> 00:20:49,519
could cost him everything.

366
00:20:50,359 --> 00:20:52,079
If Qi Feng truly was the water ghost,

367
00:20:52,599 --> 00:20:53,599
then Sun Qi and the other two

368
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:56,000
must have been connected
to the sinking of the Qi family's ship.

369
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:57,519
Di!

370
00:20:58,720 --> 00:20:59,519
Di!

371
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:05,640
Two years ago,

372
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:07,720
on the ship that sank
with the Qi family,

373
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:09,240
Sun Qi handled the transport orders,

374
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,599
Liu Shun was one of the dock laborers,

375
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:12,400
and Jia Gui handled ship repairs.

376
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,000
In the half month

377
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,039
after the ship sank,

378
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,480
Sun Qi bought a house,

379
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,880
Liu Shun got married,

380
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,640
and Jia Gui

381
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,799
opened his own carpentry shop.

382
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,720
You even managed to find all that out.

383
00:21:22,720 --> 00:21:24,559
No one handles this kind of work
better than Duan.

384
00:21:24,599 --> 00:21:25,960
Naturally.

385
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:28,039
The sinking of the ship

386
00:21:28,039 --> 00:21:29,799
must be connected to Wang Dingrong.

387
00:21:30,359 --> 00:21:31,799
But it has already been two years.

388
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:34,079
The evidence is probably gone by now.

389
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:36,519
The most urgent matter
is Qi Feng's death.

390
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:38,319
Tell Magistrate Cao

391
00:21:38,519 --> 00:21:40,079
to find the arsonists
as soon as possible.

392
00:21:40,119 --> 00:21:40,440
Duan.

393
00:21:40,519 --> 00:21:40,759
Hm?

394
00:21:41,039 --> 00:21:42,519
The docks are crowded
and full of gossip.

395
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,319
Go investigate.

396
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:44,000
Understood.

397
00:21:52,119 --> 00:21:52,920
My mother said

398
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:54,319
there's a water ghost in the river.

399
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,880
She told me not to come near it.

400
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:57,680
If she finds out,

401
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:59,279
she'll beat me senseless.

402
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:01,119
We'll spear two fish
and head right back.

403
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:01,960
What are you afraid of?

404
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:03,480
It's not like you've never seen

405
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:04,960
my fishing skills before.

406
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:06,079
I never miss.

407
00:22:06,119 --> 00:22:07,279
It won't take long.

408
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:13,640
Look.

409
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:15,880
Whose clothes fell into the river?

410
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:33,960
(Preview of Next Episode)

411
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:34,799
Young...

412
00:22:35,079 --> 00:22:35,920
Young Master.

413
00:22:36,119 --> 00:22:37,640
Young...

414
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:50,599
Go.

415
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:52,480
Light it.

416
00:22:54,759 --> 00:22:55,799
You do it.

417
00:23:05,631 --> 00:23:07,211
♪Night covers the long streets♪

418
00:23:08,291 --> 00:23:10,001
♪The city remains silent♪

419
00:23:11,391 --> 00:23:12,981
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

420
00:23:13,241 --> 00:23:15,481
♪Words still left unspoken♪

421
00:23:16,881 --> 00:23:18,521
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

422
00:23:19,651 --> 00:23:22,121
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

423
00:23:22,741 --> 00:23:24,221
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

424
00:23:24,221 --> 00:23:27,361
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

425
00:23:27,981 --> 00:23:29,901
♪Love is born from desire♪

426
00:23:30,591 --> 00:23:32,721
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

427
00:23:33,861 --> 00:23:35,521
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

428
00:23:35,521 --> 00:23:38,821
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

429
00:23:40,271 --> 00:23:41,591
♪Someone once warned me♪

430
00:23:41,591 --> 00:23:43,111
♪To stop upon this shore♪

431
00:23:43,111 --> 00:23:44,431
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

432
00:23:44,431 --> 00:23:45,921
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

433
00:23:45,921 --> 00:23:47,041
♪If one thought retreats♪

434
00:23:47,041 --> 00:23:48,341
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

435
00:23:48,341 --> 00:23:49,681
♪But in this world♪

436
00:23:49,681 --> 00:23:52,081
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

437
00:23:53,911 --> 00:23:56,721
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

438
00:23:56,721 --> 00:23:58,191
♪Still I walk ahead♪

439
00:23:58,421 --> 00:23:59,641
♪Let it pierce through♪

440
00:23:59,641 --> 00:24:04,381
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

441
00:24:04,381 --> 00:24:06,621
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

442
00:24:06,621 --> 00:24:08,021
♪Covering every heart♪

443
00:24:08,021 --> 00:24:09,211
♪How many people♪

444
00:24:09,471 --> 00:24:10,841
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

445
00:24:10,841 --> 00:24:13,051
♪Yet call it♪

446
00:24:13,251 --> 00:24:14,591
♪Fate?♪

447
00:24:14,951 --> 00:24:16,131
♪Life and death♪

448
00:24:16,131 --> 00:24:17,391
♪Balanced on a single line♪

449
00:24:17,741 --> 00:24:18,911
♪Light and shadow♪

450
00:24:18,911 --> 00:24:20,171
♪Hanging side by side♪

451
00:24:20,171 --> 00:24:21,651
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

452
00:24:21,651 --> 00:24:23,061
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

453
00:24:23,061 --> 00:24:24,601
♪In the end, it is only♪

454
00:24:24,601 --> 00:24:25,981
♪A single misguided thought♪

455
00:24:25,981 --> 00:24:27,541
♪If unveiling the truth♪

456
00:24:27,541 --> 00:24:28,881
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

457
00:24:28,881 --> 00:24:30,051
♪Then this answer♪

458
00:24:30,051 --> 00:24:31,411
♪Can it still remain true?♪

459
00:24:31,411 --> 00:24:32,811
♪When love and law♪

460
00:24:32,811 --> 00:24:34,291
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

461
00:24:34,291 --> 00:24:35,691
♪Which figure before me♪

462
00:24:35,691 --> 00:24:42,891
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

463
00:24:42,891 --> 00:24:45,621
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

464
00:24:45,621 --> 00:24:47,211
♪Still I walk ahead♪

465
00:24:47,211 --> 00:24:48,451
♪Not for fame or glory♪

466
00:24:48,451 --> 00:24:53,321
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

467
00:24:53,321 --> 00:24:55,131
♪Human nature is clouded♪

468
00:24:55,131 --> 00:24:56,851
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

469
00:24:56,851 --> 00:24:58,321
♪Though this world♪

470
00:24:58,321 --> 00:24:59,691
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

471
00:24:59,691 --> 00:25:01,941
♪There is still a light♪

472
00:25:01,941 --> 00:25:04,901
♪Worth pursuing♪

473
00:25:04,901 --> 00:25:06,721
♪Every case has its ending♪

474
00:25:06,721 --> 00:25:07,981
♪But night does not always fade♪

475
00:25:08,251 --> 00:25:09,631
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

476
00:25:09,631 --> 00:25:10,851
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

477
00:25:11,121 --> 00:25:12,201
♪If justice stands♪

478
00:25:12,201 --> 00:25:13,451
♪Without mercy beside it♪

479
00:25:13,451 --> 00:25:15,251
♪Then how is it♪

480
00:25:15,251 --> 00:25:24,811
♪Any different from a blade?♪

481
00:25:24,811 --> 00:25:28,001
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

482
00:25:28,001 --> 00:25:29,481
♪Still I walk ahead♪

483
00:25:29,481 --> 00:25:30,871
♪Even if the world♪

484
00:25:30,871 --> 00:25:35,601
♪Refuses to answer♪

485
00:25:35,601 --> 00:25:37,561
♪When every hidden truth♪

486
00:25:37,561 --> 00:25:39,271
♪Finally reveals itself♪

487
00:25:39,271 --> 00:25:40,631
♪I only wish♪

488
00:25:40,631 --> 00:25:42,111
♪To hold on♪

489
00:25:42,111 --> 00:25:46,851
♪Within the darkness♪

490
00:25:46,851 --> 00:25:48,851
♪To the heart♪

